p n^{- \\alpha / d}.$$ We also obtained the\nasymptotic order of quantities of optimal recovery by $S_n^B$ in terms of best\n$n$-term approximation as well of other non-linear $n$-widths.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 17 Feb 2011 10:09:09 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 26 Feb 2011 07:21:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2011-03-01"}
